## get ##

**Interface:** `/cache/get`

**Method:** `GET`

**Parameter:** 

*  **key** (Required)

This Interface is an proxy interface for `/hustcache/get`. See more details in [here](../../hustdb/hustcache/get.md).  

**Sample:**

    curl -i -X GET "http://localhost:8082/cache/get?key=test_key"
